               (df/prepend-to [:b 2 :g])))) => #{[:a 1] [:b 2] [:c 3] :x}
      "Adds the target's first two elements as an ident to refresh (when target has 2+ elements)"
      (set (#'df/computed-refresh [:a] :b [:x 3 :boo])) => #{:a [:x 3]}
      (set (#'df/computed-refresh [:a] :b [:x 3])) => #{:a [:x 3]}
